{"word":"ἔρομαι","slug":"ἔρομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἔρομαι</b></el> <p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to ask, enquire</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> objecti, <i>to learn by enquiry</i>, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b>: <i>to ask after</i> or <i>for</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <a href='S:person, personal'>pers.</a> <i>to enquire of, question</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>,<p/></div><div class='li750'><b>4. </b><a href='S:cum'>c.</a> dupl. <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> <i>to ask</i> one <i>about</i> a thing, <b><a href='S:Odyssey'>Od.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}